channel.title: Cannot delete file: Cannot read from the source or disk
channel.description:
When I try to delete an account called MySqlBot : which as an account that was crashing my server it gives me this error: Cannot delete file: Cannot read from the source or disk.
is there any way I can delete it?

Then just put this in it

@echo off
del MySqlBot
pause

And save as delete.bat run it and it should delete it…

item.title: Cannot delete file: Cannot read from the source or disk
item.dc:creator: @InfoManiac InfoManiac
item.description:
@InfoManiac wrote:

No…

Open notepad and put this in it.

@echo off
del MySqlBot.txt
pause

Save it as Delete.bat

Put it in your character folder and that should work.
